                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-262-off1387 t18280221-262-cd1389"></join>, 1824; I occasionally employed him to collect money; I told him on that day to receive 1l. 16s. 6d. from Tucker - he should have brought me the money the same morning; I never saw him afterwards till he was taken, and have never received the money.</p>
